805
00:43:39,411 --> 00:43:41,871
- I'm sure "The Lancet" article
garnered some attention.

806
00:43:41,913 --> 00:43:43,873
- Yes, we can capitalize
on that momentum

807
00:43:43,915 --> 00:43:45,834
