810
00:43:50,880 --> 00:43:53,174
- Around and around.

811
00:43:53,216 --> 00:43:55,677
- Until we can expand...

812
00:43:55,719 --> 00:43:58,054
globally.

813
00:43:58,096 --> 00:44:01,474
